{"word":"περιέχω","slug":"περιέχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>περιέχω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:περί\">περί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔχω\">ἔχω</a></el>] ‘have in possession’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of an emotional experience <b>take hold of <a href='B:490 5:9'>Lk 5:9</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> sense, of a document <b>contain <a href='B:510 15:23'>Ac 15:23</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:510 23:25'>23:25</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>;</b> <el>π. <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a> γραφῇ</el> it’s there in (sacred) writing <b><a href='B:670 2:6'>1 Pt 2:6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:περιέτεμον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:περιζώννυμι/περιζωννύω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}